md:name.md:partName: Mūsa ibn Muhammad Mahmūd al-Rūmī Qadīzade (d. 815 H [1412] / 840 H [1436])
Šarh [kitāb] al-Ğiġmīni [or Šarh al-Mulahhas fī al-hay’ah]]

div.p: Teksten er en kommentar til det astronomiske kompendium al-Mulahhas fī al-hay'ah skrevet af Mahmūd ibn Muhammad ibn 'Umar al-Ğiġmīni al Hwarizmi (d. efter 618 H [1221]).
I margen ses Al-Masiyah [ala Šarh mulahhas al-Ğiġmīni li-Qādizāde] skrevet af Abd al-'Alī [al-]Birğandī (d. efter 935 H [1528]). Dette er en kommentar til Šarh [kitāb] al-Giġmīni.
Beskrevet i: Catalogue of Arabic Manuscripts. Codices Arabici Arthur Christenseniani af Irmeli Perho. Copenhagen. Det Kongelige Bibliotek, 2003, s. 1-5.
The text is a commentary to the astronomical compendium al-Mulahhas fī al-hay'ah written by Mahmūd ibn Muhammad ibn 'Umar al-Ğiġmīni al Hwarizmi (d. after 618 H [1221]).
In the margins one can find the supercommentary of Šarh [kitāb]al-Ğiġmīni: Al-Masiyah [ala Šarh mulahhas al-Ğiġmīni li-Qādizāde] written by Abd al-'Alī [al-]Birğandī (d. after 935 H [1528 CE]).
Described in: Catalogue of Arabic Manuscripts. Codices Arabici Arthur Christenseniani by Irmeli Perho. Copenhagen. Det Kongelige Bibliotek, 2003, pp. 1-5.
